parameters.name: BR
parameters.description: Column contains radial (Jupiter to spacecraft) component of the magnetic field vector in units of nanoTelsa (nT).

parameters.name: BTHETA
parameters.description: Column contains the North/South (system III) component of the magnetic field vector (positive southward). Units are nanoTelsa (nT).

parameters.name: BPHI
parameters.description: Column contains the azimuthal (system III) component of the magnetic field vector (positive eastward). Units are nanoTesla (nT).

parameters.name: BMAG
parameters.description: Column contains average of the magnetic field magnitude.
